58:23.666 --> 58:24.708
Climb up here.

58:35.625 --> 58:38.416
- Guima, this is crazy!
- Awesome, right?

58:39.708 --> 58:41.500
It's like a dream!

58:42.291 --> 58:45.208
Yeah. I said Carnaval was magic.

59:10.916 --> 59:12.916
Hey, what's up? Sorry!

59:13.000 --> 59:14.625
Tavinho, for God's sake!

59:14.708 --> 59:16.000
