59:16.083 --> 59:17.333
- Clothes off.
- What?

59:17.416 --> 59:18.541
Take your clothes off.

59:18.625 --> 59:21.333
Phone and things in here.
I'll keep them for you.

59:22.208 --> 59:23.500
Here's your leotard.

59:23.583 --> 59:25.750
- Leotard?
- Emanuel, paint him, please.

59:25.833 --> 59:27.625
- Great. Tavinho, right?
- Tavinho.

59:27.708 --> 59:29.125
- Clothes off.
- What?

59:29.208 --> 59:31.541
For your makeup! Clothes off.

59:33.291 --> 59:36.250
